{"type": "article", "id": 3070, "title": "Sudare 户外家具系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-27T08:05:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233028C4dwYDfjiAr5S6yP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNendo 近来连出家具新品，日前带来的最新户外家具系列，名为 Sudare 。这是 Nendo 为日本家具品牌 PATIO PETITE 专属定做的产品，以木头材质的百叶窗结构为主要设计元素，制作出各种模块化的桌子、椅子以及屏风等。Sudare 系列最大的特点在于其富于变化的外型，铺开时可以作为餐桌、椅子等使用，而折叠起来它就是一面屏风。桌椅之外,Nendo 还为 Sudare 系列设计了便于户外野餐时使用的托盘与碗等容器。Sudare 系列提供 5 种不同颜色以及两种天然饰面材质的选择。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233026IH2eVhQLmFo5rBkN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233026q598y6AVDaFpeHKI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330260p7FWC4QjhT5OAZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330275Xdlvk1nMcErOYQJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233027BoRq84KTsdQGWADI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233027UEvtzQeBCF1cK5sk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}